query: SELECT pc.*, p.name as productName, c.name as categoryName FROM product_categories pc JOIN products p ON pc.productId = p.id JOIN categories c ON pc.categoryId = c.id WHERE LOWER(p.name) LIKE '%vanguard%' LIMIT 10;
